						<p>In Vaṭṭeḻuttu characters. Damaged. Records a gift of money by Anantavīra-aḍigaḷ for a lamp to (the Jaina shrine of) Tirukkuṇagiridēva. The trustees of the <hi rend="italic">Paḷḷi</hi> were asked to protect the gift.</p>						

